        "text": "R.M. Horton, H.D. Hunt, S.N. Ho, J.K. Pullen, L.R. Pease, Engineering hybrid genes without the use of restriction enzymes: gene splicing by overlap extension, Gene 77 (1989) 61-68.",
        "bbox": [
